casebody.data:
RIEGER, Respondent, v. SWAN, Appellant. (Common Pleas of New York City and County,

General Term.

May 8, 1893.) Action by John H. Rieger against William J. Swan.

Argued before BOOKSTAVER, BISCHOFF, and PRYOR, JJ.

No opinion. Motion for reargument denied, with $10 costs. See 22 N. Y. Supp. 1128.
